{
  "stem": "10353.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "By the time I came down from the third floor, I was already caught in a trap.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I couldn't go out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Some people escaped and Wallenberg took them away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Around 10 o'clock or so, we were ordered to march down and to line up, which we did.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "We were lined up and we started to be marched toward the railway station.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And the railway station-- we arrived at the railway station still under heavy guard.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "We were lined up in rows and [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we were broken up in groups of 70 and we marched-- we were put in 70 people per freight car.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All men.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All men.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Young men, middle-aged men.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this procedure was taking on practically most of the day.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And towards nightfall, the train moved out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now, we were traveling on that train, no food, no nothing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But once we were put into the freight cars, there were some young Zionists.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "How they got there, I don't know, but they were distributing cans of marmalade.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That's all they had.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So for every freight car, they put in so many cans of marmalade.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We were traveling-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Sunday, Monday, Tuesday, Wednesday, Thursday, Friday.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We were traveling 'til the following Sunday morning, when we reached-- when we reached the Austrian border.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Monday night, Tuesday, Wednesday, Thursday, Friday, Saturday.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Five days 'til we reached the Austrian border.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This is usually a distance that actually should take only about a half a day to three quarters of a day, but they kept on sidelining us-- sidelining us because military trains were going back and forth.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then at the Austrian border, we were given a little piece of bread, part of a bread, and some cheese.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was the first food we got.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Luckily, some people had some food acquired you know, there in the orphanage, you know, could acquire some food.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We were-- we were at the border for maybe a few hours.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then the train took off and we were traveling into Germany.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] No water.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Everybody was very thirsty.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "No water.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "No toilet facilities.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "People made holes in the-- in the floor.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then there were little windows.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "People were held.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Two or three people would hold people to try to relieve themselves.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was an awful sight. 70 people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We were cramped.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You couldn't sleep.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "When you got up in the morning, you find one leg, one side and 10 people sleeping on it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And this was going on like that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But we didn't get no water.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "People were very thirsty.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And as it happened, the train-- the water came through the wagons, the freight car's roof.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "People were standing there and fighting for the drops of water.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And 'til-- we traveled 'til about Tuesday evening.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Finally, on Tuesday evening, we were already in Germany when the SS-- we were stopped at a railway station and they gave a bucket of water for each wagon.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So you can imagine the fight that was going on for that little bit of water.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It wasn't 'til the following Thursday morning we woke up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We were in Germany.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "The train was stopped.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And we were-- we were ordered to get out of the freight cars.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We were marched out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We were again put into columns.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And we were started to be marched for a distance.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We saw the sign Bergen-Belsen.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And that was our first inclination that we are in a concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "We came into Bergen-Belsen and [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they lined us up again in columns.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And the SS with their dogs were running up and down with canes beating-- beatings everybody.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I was anointed with my first beating there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And it took them time to put us in order.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "We were-- we were about-- by that time, we were about more than 4,000 people on that train, 4,500 people.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "We were marched into a tent, a huge tent where there were two SS sitting there on either side with tails.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] you had to surrender anything that you had.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Now, to backtrack, prior to getting to Bergen-Belsen, the freight car doors opened up and the orders came from the SS, anybody that has any watches, gold pieces should surrender it or else they will be shot on site.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "So that was the first confiscation.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "When we arrived in Bergen-Belsen, we were marched to this tent.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And you had a little knapsack.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "You had some things in your pocket, whatever, had to-- you had to surrender before you got-- first you got a beating and then you had to surrender all those things and march through empty-handed.",
      "word_count": 35
    }
  ],
